Skip Stephenson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skip_Stephenson 0 Charles Frederick "Skip" Stephenson (April 18, 1940 – May 18, 1992) was an American actor, comedian, and musician. He was born in Omaha, Nebraska, and graduated in 1958 from Holy Name High School. After attending a year at The University of Omaha, Stephenson took a job as a DJ in Alliance, Nebraska.
